WEBVTT

00:11:59.837 --> 00:12:03.749
"We're going to go get coffee."

00:12:03.749 --> 00:12:06.890
And they left.

00:12:06.890 --> 00:12:09.725
Tell me three things about
yourself before the next stop.

00:12:09.725 --> 00:12:12.481
People were leaving the bus before she even got

00:12:12.481 --> 00:12:17.858
to number two or number three.

00:12:17.858 --> 00:12:21.345
So I handed her a tissue,

00:12:21.345 --> 00:12:24.642
and I gave her a hug,

00:12:24.642 --> 00:12:28.152
and then, because I really cared for this woman,

00:12:28.152 --> 00:12:30.238
I said,